author: stsp
msg: Add a prelimenary version of a new 'svnauth' tool.
This tool will manage the authentication credentials cache.
Currently, svnauth supports listing available cache types (svnauth --version)
and listing cached credentials (svnauth list). The list of credentials is
not formatted nicely yet. I hope to improve this soon.
Support for removing cached credentials will be added later, too.
I'd also like to add support for listing cached client and server SSL
certificates in a useful way, and allow to delete them.
* subversion/svnauth/svnauth.1: New man page. Based on svnadmin man page.
* subversion/svnauth/svnauth.c: New tool. Code partly based on svn and svnadmin.
